title: Bully (Live on KEXP at Home)
description: Bully's Alicia Bognanno shares a set of songs recorded at home from her forthcoming album, SUGAREGG, and joins KEXP DJ Abbie Gobeli on Tuesday, August 11, at 3pm PT.
